{
  "text": "When did the first call occur and how did it occur? The first calling was approximately a four six thousand, a forty six thousand of your years ago. This calling was of those of Maldek. These entities were aware of their need for rectifying the consequences of their action and were in some confusion in an incarnate state as to the circumstances of their incarnation, the unconscious being aware, the conscious being quite confused. This created a calling. The Confederation sent love and light to these entities.",
